                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Hardware</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                                Digital systems, analog systems, mixed-signal systems, and power systems.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Circuit design</li>
                                <li>• PCB layout</li>
                                <li>• BOM optimization</li>
                                <li>• DFM/DFA/DFC/DFT</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:bg-white transition-all duration-200">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Firmware</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                                Embedded firmware and real-time control systems.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                                <li>• Real-time systems</li>
                                <li>• Power optimization</li>
                                <li>• Control algorithms</li>
                                <li>• Wireless connectivity</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:bg-white transition-all duration-200">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Testing & Validation</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                                System bring-up, validation, and regulatory compliance testing.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                                <li>• System bring-up</li>
                                <li>• Debugging and validation</li>
                                <li>• EMC testing</li>
                                <li>• Regulatory compliance</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

