                      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">15+ years embedded systems • Former team lead at medical device and industrial automation companies</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                      <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Medical Device Experience</h4>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                          <li>• Led hardware teams on 12+ FDA 510(k) submissions</li>
                          <li>• IEC 60601 compliance for imaging and diagnostic devices</li>
                          <li>• EMC testing and signal integrity optimization</li>
