                        </ul>
                      </div>

                      <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Industrial & Scientific</h4>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                          <li>• CE marking for industrial safety systems</li>
                          <li>• Power electronics and motor control</li>
                          <li>• Scientific instrument modernization</li>
                          <li>• Wireless connectivity and IoT integration</li>
                        </ul>
